  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK333">
<l>aṟkā viyalpiṟṟuc celva matupeṟṟā</l>
<l>laṟkupa vāṅkē ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wealth is perishable let those who obtain it immediately practise those (virtues) which are imperishable.</l>
            </lg>
